## JSON-RPC 2.0 Протокол

### Структура запросов

MCP использует JSON-RPC 2.0, НЕ REST:

<good_example>
# Initialize
POST https://mcp.example.com/mcp
Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  Accept: application/json, text/event-stream
  Mcp-Session-Id: {uuid}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": {"name": "agent-lab", "version": "1.0.0"}
  }
}

# List tools
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/list"
}

# Call tool
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "tool-name",
    "arguments": {"param": "value"}
  }
}
</good_example>

<bad_example>
# НЕ используй REST endpoints
POST /list_tools  # ❌
POST /call_tool   # ❌

# Правильно - JSON-RPC метод
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "tools/list"  # ✅
}
</bad_example>

